                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-74-off376 t18270531-74-cd377"></join>, 3 pairs of trousers, value 8s., and 1 pair of half-boots, value 4s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18270531-74-victim524" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Brewer
               <interp inst="t18270531-74-victim524" type="surname" value="Brewer"></interp>
